# Color
### Accepted Data Type(s)
- String
### Accepted Color color models
- HEX
- RGB
- HSL
### Usage
```lua
local hexColor = '#ff3300'
local rgbColor = 'rgb(255, 51, 0)'
local hslColor = 'hsl(12, 100%, 50%)'
```

